{"name": "fourdigits-cli", "metadata": {"name": "fourdigits-cli", "version": "1.18.0", "classifiers": [], "home_page": null, "license": null, "documentation_url": null, "dependencies": ["click", "tomli", "fabric", "packaging", "requests", "watchdog"], "summary": "FourDigits CLI tool", "upload_time": 1734422593}, "documentation": ["# FourDigits CLI\n\nA command line tool to make development and deployment easier within Four Digits.\n\nIt has the following commands:\n\n1. \"docker\"\n    - \"build\": Build docker images in our Gitlab CI pipelines\n    - \"tag\": Create new Docker tag for existing Docker tag on registry\n2. \"gitlab\"\n    - \"fix-coverage-paths\": Change the generated coverage.xml so Gitlab can show coverage visualization in merge requests\n3. \"exonet\"\n   - \"deploy\": Deploy a project to Exonet\n   - \"db:download\": Download a database from Exonet and import it locally\n   - \"db:copy\": Copy a database from one environment to another\n4. \"docker-compose\"\n   - \"sync\": Sync files from a service to local folder\n   - \"sync:env\": Shortcut for django:home/userapp/env -> env-docker\n\n## Install\n\nWith [pipx](https://github.com/pypa/pipx):\n\n    pipx install fourdigits-cli\n\nWith [pip](https://github.com/pypa/pip):\n\n    sudo pip install --break-system-packages fourdigits-cli\n\n## Upgrade\n\nWith pipx:\n\n    pipx upgrade fourdigits-cli\n\nWith pip:\n\n    sudo pip install --upgrade fourdigits-cli\n\n### Enable auto complete\n\n#### bash\n\nAdd this to `~/.bashrc`:\n\n```shell\neval \"$(_4D_COMPLETE=bash_source 4d)\"\neval \"$(_FOURDIGITS_COMPLETE=bash_source fourdigits)\"\n```\n\n#### Zsh\n\nAdd this to `~/.zshrc`:\n\n```shell\neval \"$(_4D_COMPLETE=zsh_source 4d)\"\neval \"$(_FOURDIGITS_COMPLETE=zsh_source fourdigits)\"\n```\n\n## Usage\n\nAfter installation the cli tool is available under `fourdigits` and `4d`.\nFor more information use:\n\n    fourdigits --help\n\n### Example: Build a docker image and deploy it to the test environment\n\nBuild an image for the `tst` environment and upload it to our registry:\n\n```\n$ fourdigits docker build tst --push\nDocker build image <docker_tag>\n - file=Dockerfile\n - context=.\n - target=None\nDocker create tag <tmp_tag> -> docker-registry.fourdigits.nl/fourdigits/<project>:tst\nDocker push tag docker-registry.fourdigits.nl/fourdigits/<project>:tst\nDocker create tag <tmp_tag> -> docker-registry.fourdigits.nl/fourdigits/<project>:<docker_tag>\nDocker push tag docker-registry.fourdigits.nl/fourdigits/wijsproductportals:<docker_tag>\n```\n\nTo deploy this to the `tst` environment, use the `docker_tag` (not the `tmp_tag`) from the previous step:\n\n```bash\n$ fourdigits exonet deploy tst <docker_tag>\n{\"id\":...,\"number\":<number>,...}\n```\n\nYou can see the progress of the deployment pipeline on https://drone.exonet.nl/exonet/containers-fourdigits/<number>. \n\n## Troubleshooting\n\n### unauthorized\n\nIf you get:\n```\nunauthorized: unauthorized to access repository: fourdigits/<project>, action: push: unauthorized to access repository: fourdigits/<project>, action: push\n```\n\nYou need to login to the registry:\n\n```bash\ndocker login\ndocker login docker-registry.fourdigits.nl\n```\n\n## Project configuration\n\nThe project is configured in the `pyproject.toml` file, available options and their defaults:\n\n```toml\n[project]\nname = \"default-project\"\n\n[tool.fourdigits]\nexonet_project_name=\"<default is project name>\"\ndocker_repo=\"<default is project name>\"\nslack_channel=\"<default is project name>\"\ndocker_image_user=\"fourdigits\"\n\n[tool.fourdigits.envs.<environment anem>]\nexonet_environment=\"<default is environment name>\"\n# Every setting can be overridden per environment\nslack_channel=\"custom-channel\"\n```\n\n### Example project with separate nextjs\n\n```toml\n[project]\nname = \"django-project\"\n\n[tool.fourdigits]\n# default to project name\n\n[tool.fourdigits.envs.tst]\n\n[tool.fourdigits.envs.acc]\n\n[tool.fourdigits.envs.prd]\n\n[tool.fourdigits.envs.nextjs_tst]\nexonet_project_name = \"nextjs\"\nexonet_environment = \"tst\"\ndocker_repo = \"nextjs\"\n\n[tool.fourdigits.envs.nextjs_acc]\nexonet_project_name = \"nextjs\"\nexonet_environment = \"acc\"\ndocker_repo = \"nextjs\"\n\n[tool.fourdigits.envs.nextjs_prd]\nexonet_project_name = \"nextjs\"\nexonet_environment = \"prd\"\ndocker_repo = \"nextjs\"\n```\n\n## Development\n\n    make develop\n\n## Releasing\n\nTo make a new release available on pypi, follow these steps:\n\n1. Update version by edit `fourdigits_cli/__init__.py` and commit.\n2. Run: `make push-version`\n3. Update the installation of fourdigits-cli in https://gitlab.com/fourdigits/utils/docker-pipeline-image/-/blob/main/Dockerfile\nto the newest version.\n"], "modules": [{"name": "fourdigits_cli", "documentation": [], "functions": [], "variables": [{"name": "fourdigits_cli.__version__", "type": null, "documentation": []}], "classes": [], "exports": []}, {"name": "fourdigits_cli.cli", "documentation": [], "functions": [{"name": "fourdigits_cli.cli.main", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "debug", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}], "variables": [], "classes": [], "exports": []}, {"name": "fourdigits_cli.commands", "documentation": [], "functions": [], "variables": [], "classes": [], "exports": []}, {"name": "fourdigits_cli.commands.gitlab", "documentation": [], "functions": [{"name": "fourdigits_cli.commands.gitlab.group", "asynchronous": false, "params": [], "returns": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "fourdigits_cli.commands.gitlab.fix_coverage_paths", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "path", "type": null, "default": "..."}, {"name": "path_prefix", "type": null, "default": "..."}, {"name": "fail_silent", "type": null, "default": "..."}], "returns": null, "documentation": ["Add prefix to all filenames in given coverage xml,\nto fix gitlab pull request coverage visualization.\nThis is needed if you run your coverage from a subdirectory,\nlike docker compose with a src folder.\n\nPATH: defaults to src/coverage.xml"]}, {"name": "fourdigits_cli.commands.gitlab.raise_error_or_exit_silently", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "message", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "silent", "type": null, "default": "..."}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}], "variables": [], "classes": [], "exports": []}, {"name": "fourdigits_cli.commands.docker", "documentation": [], "functions": [{"name": "fourdigits_cli.commands.docker.group", "asynchronous": false, "params": [], "returns": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "fourdigits_cli.commands.docker.build", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "environment", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "**options", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "fourdigits_cli.commands.docker.tag", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "src_tag", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "new_tag", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "**options", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "fourdigits_cli.commands.docker.do_build", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "docker", "type": {"name": "Docker", "xref": {"fqname": "fourdigits_cli.utils.docker.Docker", "project": null}, "params": null}, "default": null}, {"name": "image", "type": {"name": "str", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.str", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "default": null}, {"name": "no_rebuild", "type": {"name": "bool", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.bool", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "fourdigits_cli.commands.docker.validate_and_get_version", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "environment", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "version", "type": null, "default": "..."}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "fourdigits_cli.commands.docker.validate_version", "as